location.fullValue: Palmetto Plan, Trails at Grassy Creek

data.description: This exquisite and lovely home boasts 4045 sf, 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths, with an amazing, updated kitchen with granite counter tops, a center island, double ovens, canned lighting, tile backsplash, and stainless appliances. There is also a large walk-in pantry with new LVP flooring. Separate dining room and den/office on the main floor. All the bedrooms are upstairs and are large with walk-in closets. You will gasp when you see the fabulous owner's bedroom, with a vaulted ceiling, "his and her's" expansive walk-in closet, private bath with double sinks, separate shower and garden tub. All the other 3 bedrooms are extremely large and spacious and each has a walk-in closet. You'll have several areas for the family to gather - a living room, family room or the large-open loft upstairs. The composite roof was replaced in 2022 along with the soffit/gutters and vinyl siding. The exterior air compressor was replaced in 2015. Vinyl, privacy fence encloses the backyard area.  There is also a three-car attached garage and a large enough driveway for 3 additional vehicles. There is a large concrete patio in the backyard with lots of room for kids to play or entertaining guests. The newer Jacuzzi stays, has blue tooth tech and you can listen to music while soaking your troubles away.
